definitions.definition: To travel , often instantaneously , from one point to another without physically crossing the distance between the two points.
To move (an object) in this fashion, as by telekinesis .

main_definition: ( intransitive ) To travel , often instantaneously , from one point to another without physically crossing the distance between the two points.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive ) To move (an object) in this fashion, as by telekinesis .
